  <p>Artificial intelligence isn't just a buzzword anymore — it's a money-making machine for anyone willing to learn how to use it. If you've been wondering how to make money with AI tools in 2026, you're asking the right question at the right time. The AI economy has exploded, and opportunities are everywhere for freelancers, entrepreneurs, and side hustlers alike.</p>
